{"tid":184190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線科技人員：疑似濫用選民登記資料 宣傳單張地址區議會選區","createTime":"2017-04-02T15:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T16:06:01.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5aa6d530b231a07177565e47c30886a0554c9ae1","tid":184190,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"前線科技人員<br />\n<br />\n#疑似濫用選民登記資料 有資訊科技界嘅選民同我哋報料，話佢早前以到一間叫做 DigiKey 嘅公司所寄嚟嘅宣傳單張。本來收到宣傳單張並唔值得奇怪，但特別嘅係，單張所用嘅地址係一個佢平時唔會用嘅寫法，因為包含咗區議會選區 FU NAM （富藍）一詞，據報料人所講，除咗登記選民資料外，佢絕對唔會係第二 D 地方用呢個寫法，因此有理由懷疑，呢間公司係不法地利用佢嘅選民資料去做商業宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇其他資訊科技界嘅選民收到同樣嘅宣傳資料呢？有嘅話麻煩留言，或者 PM 我哋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17457539_1467648106608251_1164521648973602349_n.png?oh=9f34361fc5cacd5589ac9cd116b1ebab&amp;oe=5953370C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17457539_1467648106608251_1164521648973602349_n.png%3Foh%3D9f34361fc5cacd5589ac9cd116b1ebab%26oe%3D5953370C&h=2b7a9040&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3535ab6811155a56db158a515508989e9c63ab5","tid":184190,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:37:47.000Z","msg":"//Fu Nam 富藍實乃區議會選區Q22，包括富寧花園及蔚藍灣畔，現實生活中沒有人用此稱呼。//"},{"pid":"2c7576b9b2d14fafa2bac5bfe9d48644bcfd0298","tid":184190,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:39:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b823f67cbc036db6f8470cbc8ef6559eda6e63b","tid":184190,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:39:39.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"85fef55569fd06e51026d9a63145b1862a8269cc","tid":184190,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:51:15.000Z","msg":"我屋企有人係工程界, <br />\n富君區 (富康+君傲灣)<br />\n都收到同一張野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FRdYbD9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFRdYbD9.jpg&h=615af063&s={SIZE}\" />"},